      <title>美国称在南海护航菲律宾船只是一种选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/us-says-escorting-philippine-ships-in-south-china-sea-an-option</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级军事官员称，在菲律宾船只与中国船只频频发生对峙的情况下，美国愿意在有争议的南海地区陪同菲律宾船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/us-says-escorting-philippine-ships-in-south-china-sea-an-option</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默警告重建英国公共财政的预算“痛苦”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/starmer-warns-of-painful-budget-to-rebuild-uk-public-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默警告称，其政府的十月份预算声明将是“痛苦的”，并要求人们接受“短期痛苦以换取长期利益”，首相利用其上任后的首次重要讲话为可能的增税奠定基础，以重建英国公共财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/starmer-warns-of-painful-budget-to-rebuild-uk-public-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯为警方逮捕杜特尔特牧师盟友辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/marcos-defends-police-seeking-to-arrest-duterte-s-pastor-ally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯为警方逮捕与前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特家族关系密切的牧师的行动进行辩护，这是该国两个最强大家族之间最新的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/marcos-defends-police-seeking-to-arrest-duterte-s-pastor-ally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:30:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登顾问会见中国高级外交官以缓解紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/biden-s-top-security-adviser-lands-in-china-for-official-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的高级国家安全助理杰克·沙利文在北京会见了中国外交部长王毅，目前世界两大经济体正寻求通过对话来管理彼此之间的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/biden-s-top-security-adviser-lands-in-china-for-official-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 05:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核监督机构开始检查俄罗斯库尔斯克核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/nuclear-agency-chief-to-lead-risk-assessment-trip-at-kursk-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国原子能机构的观察员正准备评估俄罗斯境内一座核电站的安全状况，该核电站靠近乌克兰本月在跨境入侵中占领的领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/nuclear-agency-chief-to-lead-risk-assessment-trip-at-kursk-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚对社交媒体许可计划的阻力不以为然</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/malaysia-plan-to-license-social-media-platforms-sparks-pushback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚将按计划推进其对消息和社交媒体服务提供商的监管计划，而不受业界要求政府暂时搁置此举以进一步考虑的呼声影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/malaysia-plan-to-license-social-media-platforms-sparks-pushback</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:59:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
