      <title>印度领导人访问基辅后，莫迪与拜登、普京通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/biden-modi-discussed-ukraine-after-indian-leader-s-kyiv-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪对基辅进行和解访问后，莫迪与美国总统乔·拜登和俄罗斯领导人弗拉基米尔·普京讨论了乌克兰战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/biden-modi-discussed-ukraine-after-indian-leader-s-kyiv-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 18:41:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙拒绝左翼阵营 寻求中间派法国总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/le-pen-rejects-left-wing-premier-as-france-awaits-macron-s-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙排除了由左翼候选人露西·卡斯泰领导的政府，转而支持可能的中间派联盟，周二，马克龙正在继续就任命总理一事进行磋商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/le-pen-rejects-left-wing-premier-as-france-awaits-macron-s-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国军机首次侵犯日本领空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/japan-scrambles-fighters-after-chinese-military-plane-incursion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一架中国军机闯入日本领空，这是一起史无前例的事件，引发了东京的强烈谴责，北京方面则承诺调查此事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/japan-scrambles-fighters-after-chinese-military-plane-incursion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
